\c 12
\s Abapristi lamaLevi abafika loZerubhabheli
\p
\v 1 Lalaba ngabapristi lamaLevi\x + Ezra 2.1,2.\x* abenyuka loZerubhabheli indodana kaSalatiyeli\x + 1 Lan. 3.19.\x*, loJeshuwa: OSeraya, uJeremiya, uEzra\x + Ezra 2.1,2.\x*,
\v 2 uAmariya, uMaluki, uHathushi,
\v 3 uShekaniya, uRehuma, uMeremothi,
\v 4 uIdo, uGinethoyi, uAbhiya,
\v 5 uMijamini, uMahadiya, uBiliga\x + 10.8.\x*,
\v 6 uShemaya\x + 10.8.\x*, loJoyaribi, uJedaya\x + 12.19.\x*,
\v 7 uSalu, uAmoki, uHilikhiya, uJedaya\x + 12.21.\x*. Laba babezinhloko zabapristi labafowabo ensukwini zikaJeshuwa\x + 12.1,10,26. Ezra 2.2,36. 3.2,8. 5.2. Ezra 3. 2.\x*.
\v 8 LamaLevi: OJeshuwa\x + Ezra 2.40.\x*, uBinuwi\x + Ezra 2.10.\x*, uKadimiyeli, uSherebiya, uJuda\x + Ezra 2.40.\x*, uMathaniya\x + 11.17. 12.24,25.\x*, babephezu kokubonga, yena labafowabo\x + 11.17. 12.24,25.\x*.
\v 9 LoBakibukiya loUni, abafowabo, babeqondene labo emilindweni\x + 11.17. 12.24,25.\x*.
\p
\v 10 UJeshuwa wasezala uJoyakimi\x + 12.1,10,26. Ezra 2.2,36. 3.2,8. 5.2. Ezra 3.2.\x*, uJoyakimi wasezala uEliyashibi\x + 12.22. 3.1.\x*, uEliyashibi wasezala uJoyada\x + 13.28.\x*,
\v 11 uJoyada wasezala uJonathani\x + 12.22,23.\x*, uJonathani wasezala uJaduwa\x + 12.10,26.\x*.
\v 12 Lensukwini zikaJoyakimi abapristi, inhloko zaboyise, babengo: OkaSeraya nguMeraya; okaJeremiya nguHananiya;
\v 13 okaEzra nguMeshulamu; okaAmariya nguJehohanani;
\v 14 okaMeliku nguJonathani; okaShebaniya nguJosefa;
\v 15 okaHarimi nguAdina; okaMerayothi nguHelikayi\x + Ezra 2.39.\x*;
\v 16 okaIdo nguZekhariya; okaGinethoni nguMeshulamu;
\v 17 okaAbhiya nguZikiri; okaMiniyamini, okaMowadiya nguPilitayi;
\v 18 okaBiliga nguShamuwa; okaShemaya nguJehonathani;
\v 19 lokaJoyaribi nguMathenayi; okaJedaya nguUzi\x + 12.19.\x*;
\v 20 okaSalayi nguKalayi; okaAmoki nguEberi;
\v 21 okaHilikhiya nguHashabhiya; okaJedaya nguNethaneli\x + 12.21.\x*.
